TemplateTexts.TextValue: Short evaluation of TV, Newspaper ads for a retail store viewed during product search.

HtmlItemData.Html:
Advertising Evaluation Survey
 
 
Dear Customer,
In order to help us improve your retail experience in the future, please take a few moments to complete the survey below.  Your feedback is appreciated.  Thank you.

ItemTexts_MatrixItemData.TextValue: Please indicate your evaluation of our newspaper ads:
Please indicate your evaluation of our Television ads:
Please select one answer for each of the following questions:

MatrixCategoryTexts.TextValue: How many Newspaper or Magazine ads do you remember seeing during your search for the product purchased?
How many consumer reports did you review before purchasing this product?
How many TV or Radio ads do you remember seeing during your search for the product purchased?
How many friends, relatives or neighbors did you consult while searching for this particular product?

ItemTexts_Select1Data.TextValue: Where did you last see or hear an add for our store?
What radio station do you most often listen to?
What time of day do you most often watch TV?
What Newspaper do you most often read?
Do you subscribe to Cable TV?

ItemTexts_MessageItemData.TextValue: Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey.
